data.description: BUY THIS AWESOME HOME, WE'LL BUY YOURS!* Welcome to this New Construction home! Bright, open floor plan concept. Stainless steel appliances, crisp white cabinets provides lovely contrast to backsplash in brand new kitchen. Center island for entertaining and gathering. Upgrades throughout home include: soft-close cabinets, recessed lighting, wooden blinds, and granite countertops. Spacious bedrooms with ample closet space. Beautiful master bedroom has impressive 11 ft ceiling, three closets total in master bedroom -- one walk-in and two double-door closets. Jack-and-Jill sinks in bathroom. Private fenced backyard. Attached two car garage. Front Ring doorbell, drive way and backyard cameras with timestamp features. Motion sensor alerts. Outdoor lights (sensor-sensitive solar lights) located in backyard, front yard, and side yard.
